{"tid":926071,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"抑鬱發作","createTime":"2018-12-03T07:33:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T16:18:36.000Z","uid":128275,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bde3cdd4ec422b2df7cc55965949db949ae4dea9","tid":926071,"uid":128275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T07:33:59.000Z","msg":"有冇人好似我咁<br />\n本身有抑鬱 但唔敢同另一半講<br />\n一發作就咩都做唔到<br />\n諗野好negative<br />\n野又食唔落 食完就想嘔<br />\n點先可以脫離呢個狀況<br />\n<br />\n之前有同另一半講過近排壓力大<br />\n佢就話我同佢d ex一樣<br />\n諗野負面 <br />\n又話呢個世界好多人慘過我<br />\n佢地情況仲差  一樣要面對<br />\n問返我點解唔可以好似d外國人咁正面<br />\n話兩個人要長久 <br />\n唔可以將負面情緒壓落另一方<br />\n<br />\n但係我就黎撐唔住<br />\n如果唔係驚屋企人傷心<br />\n一下就跳左落樓<br />\n我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e1e62a6f244cf0bec72b6506aff4637cbf7b081","tid":926071,"uid":198990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T08:36:25.000Z","msg":"有冇睇醫生"},{"pid":"2aed07b67e8626d1e6672c22ddcd30f8639df412","tid":926071,"uid":133528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T08:41:06.000Z","msg":"屌你老母男人老狗，互射多兩次唔好諗咁多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77d1580d53be3b352aac26067f2deeef7592c001","tid":926071,"uid":128275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e1e62a6f244cf0bec72b6506aff4637cbf7b081","tid":926071,"uid":198990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T08:36:25.000Z","msg":"有冇睇醫生"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T09:00:51.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"ceaf70aaa6eeef52899b41830060bc4365271fd6","tid":926071,"uid":201732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T16:18:36.000Z","msg":"加油!! 其實依個病好正常!<br />\n有咩隨時搵我啦!"}]}